&lt;p&gt;This role will focus on contributing to initiatives aligned to company priorities under the guidance of a Senior/Principal Product mentor. You’ll use data and customer insights to inform your decisions, write detailed product specifications and collaborate with Engineering and Design to bring ideas to life. This is a great opportunity to grow as a product thinker, communicator, and collaborator while playing a role in helping millions of travelers discover unforgettable experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
